== Tamezduɣt ==
Abeṛṛay yettidir deg yal tawennaṭ deg [[Tefrikt]] anagar idgan ama deg [[Taneẓruft|tneẓrufin]] ar [[Adrar|idurar]] yettawaṭen ar 3000 m deg teflel, anagar idgan [[Anezwu asbegsan|isbegsanen]] 

== [[Amyaraw]] d [[tarrawt]] ==
Mi ara ad tezɣel [[tawtemt|tewtemt]] tt-msegrawen (tt-nejmaɛen) fell-as i [[Awtem|iwetmen]] yerna tt-naɣen i wakken ad iwwṭen ar ɣures, Maca tawtemt tezmer ad [[Amercel|ttmercel]] d waṭas n iwtmen ɣef anect-a yiwen n wadis yezmer ad yeddem aṭas [[aqziz|iqzizen]] i waṭas n ibabaten 

[[Amercel]] n ubeṛṛay yettili-d deg wakuden yemgaraden deg useggas s unect (ɛla ḥsab) n [[anezwu|unezwu]] yellan deg temnaṭṭ anda yettidir, Amdya deg Turuft d [[Tafriqt n ugafa]] yettili-d umercel deg taggara n [[tagrest|tegrest]] (Seg [[Yennayer]] ar [[Meɣres]]) ma d [[tarrawt]] tettili-d deg [[Tafsut|Tefsut]] ([[Mayu]] s umata), [[Tadist]] n tewtemt tettaṭaf gar n 56 ar 68 n wussan tettew-d gar n yiwen n [[ammuc|ummuc]] ar 8 n immucen

